dct_description_sm: At top of sheet: "A general and particular description of Africa. Written in Latin by Joan Luyts, philos. Profess. in Acad. Ultraject."
On verso: Barbary and Bildulgerid [1:20,000,000]--A map of Zaara, Negroe-land, Guinea &c. /H. Moll fecit [1:25,000,000.] with inset: the Isles of C. Verd.
From H. Moll's A system of geography. 1701, p. 99-100.
